info.title: F5 Distributed Cloud Services API for VES.I/O.schema.shape.safeap.
info.description:
Use this API to interact with SAFE Account Protection endpoints.
All calls which not include user interaction allow a blob as the payload and return a CubeJS Structure as the return parameter.

post.description: Subscribe to Safe AP as add-on service.

401.description: Returned when operation is not authorized.

429.description: Returned when operation has been rejected as it is happening too frequently.
